<div class="NavContent" style="padding:0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align:center;"><a href="/wiki/Black_Brigades" title="Black Brigades">Black Brigades</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Blackshirts" title="Blackshirts">Blackshirts</a><br />
